'''Odupiendo racing''' was a popular sport during the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. In this fast-moving sport, flightless [[Odupiendo/Legends|Odupiendos]] raced against each other in circular tracks. The [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] was famous for its Odupiendo racing tracks. The race was a favorite betting sport in establishments such as the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="TIP1">{{SW|url=news/this-is-podracing-sports-in-the-star-wars-galaxy-part-1|series=Sports in the Star Wars Galaxy|text=Part 1: This Is Podracing|nolive=1}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
On one of the [[Viewscreen/Legends|viewscreens]] in the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]], an Odupiendo race could be witnessed. It apparently involved bipedal racing-animals running along a circular track, similar to real-life [[Horse/Legends|horse]]-racing.

